Package org.whiteflagprotocol.java

Class WfMessage.Creator

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.whiteflagprotocol.java.WfMessage.Creator
  • Enclosing class:
    WfMessage
    public static class WfMessage.Creator
extends java.lang.Object
    Whiteflag nested static message creator class

    This is a nested static builder class to create a Whiteflag message. It calls the core builder to create a message i.a.w. the Whiteflag specification.
